summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a Quitclaim Deed from the State of Washington to certain property in Tract 9, Brookvale Garden Tracts (Volume 10 of Plats, page 47, records of King County), as partial payment for certain property rights acquired by the State in City (Water Department) property for Primary State Highway No. 1 (SR 5), South 178th Street to South 126th Street.
